Package: lilim-ai
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libwebkit2gtk-4.0-37, libayatana-appindicator3-1
Maintainer: Lilith Linux <lilith@example.com>
Description: Lilim AI Assistant - Intelligent Multi-Model Routing System
 Lilim is an advanced AI assistant system featuring:
 - Multi-model routing (local and online providers)
 - System tray integration with global hotkeys
 - TTS voice synthesis (neutts-nano)
 - Screen reading capabilities (browser and terminal)
 - RAG knowledge base (Linux, Medical, Academic)
 - Agentic tool use (web search, file ops, terminal)
 .
 Global Hotkeys:
 - Ctrl+L: Toggle Lilim window
 - Ctrl+Shift+M: TTS screen reader
Installed-Size: 3500
